# 1) Deja pasar los desafíos de Let's Encrypt (ACME)
#    ¡ESTA LÍNEA DEBE IR PRIMERO!
/.well-known/*    /:splat    200!

# 2) Canonical: forzar HTTPS y dominio .com sin www
http://novamovespain.com/*        https://novamovespain.com/:splat   301!
http://www.novamovespain.com/*    https://novamovespain.com/:splat   301!
https://www.novamovespain.com/*   https://novamovespain.com/:splat   301!

# 3) Redirigir .es -> .com
http://novamovespain.es/*         https://novamovespain.com/:splat   301!
http://www.novamovespain.es/*     https://novamovespain.com/:splat   301!
https://novamovespain.es/*        https://novamovespain.com/:splat   301!
https://www.novamovespain.es/*    https://novamovespain.com/:splat   301!

# 4) Fallback SPA (React Router, etc.) — debe ir al final
